high_descs: Turn right and go to the toilet
Grab the bottle of soap off of the toilet
Back up from the toilet and look at the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can
Turn right and go to the counter between the sinks
Grab the bottle of soap off of the counter
Turn left and go to the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting two bottles of soap in the trash can

high_descs: Walk up to the wall, then turn right and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk towards the shower, the hang a left and walk forward, turn left to face the toilet.
Put the bottle of lotion in the small green bin to the left of the toilet.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, the hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the counter.
Walk back over to the small green bin to the left of the toilet.
Put the bottle of lotion into the small green bin.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion into a small green bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the brown toilet cleaner.
Turn around and return to the toilet.
Put the toilet cleaner in the green can placed on the left of the toilet.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up another brown toilet cleaner from the sink counter.
Turn left and go to the toilet.
Put the second toilet cleaner in the green can.
anns.task_desc: Put two brown toilet cleaners in a green can.
